item.title: 1 - I got my Pixel 2 XL!
item.description: I finally have my Pixel 2 XL, despite UK Mails best efforts to hide it from me. The Razer phone is available to order in the UK. Elon Musk has announcements about his new truck and roadster and I'm watching The Deuce and The Punisher this week.
item.author: mail@androidandy.uk
